Байт 04 - Timer Control Byte.
Byte 04 - Timer Control Byte

        7     6     5     4     3     2     1     0
     +-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+
     | IRQ | T1  | T2  |     unused      | T2  | T1  |
