Bytes 20-35 - Amplitude Modulation / Vibrato / Envelope Generator Type /
              Keyboard Scaling Rate / Modulator Frequency Multiple

        7     6     5     4     3     2     1     0
     +-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+
